{"tid":2078221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社︰美國將華為等20間中國企業列為受解放軍控制","createTime":"2020-06-25T01:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T07:51:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":274,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"848955f31d2b534e398b13700a133a43487a8205","tid":2078221,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:23:52.000Z","msg":"路透社報道，美國政府將20間中國大型企業，列為由中國軍方擁有或控制，當中包括電信設備商華為及視像監控公司海康威視，為美國實施新的金融制裁奠定基礎。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一份文件披露，被列為由解放軍支持、並在美國營運的公司，還包括中移動、中國電信及中航工業等，總統有權根據法律實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n國防部一名不願意透露姓名的官員，確認這份文件的真實性，又說文件已經送交國會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534021-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534021-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=dccfa5b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534021-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9a675324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534021-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b5ff27838a676759ba3bf64d17713938cb6aa296","tid":2078221,"uid":270220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"又亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7de024d10063191b470d2fcaed30c369f1c980e","tid":2078221,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"8fa86e4f3b4be9ac764804c223c19c230f6db4e0","tid":2078221,"uid":287422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"